  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Study objectives:

        -  To estimate the incidence of pulmonary deterioration in adult pulmonary Langerhans cell
           histiocytosis

        -  To assess the impact of tobacco discontinuation

        -  Study Design Multicentric prospective cohort study

        -  Main endpoint: Pulmonary deterioration

        -  Sample size : 40 patients
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Study objectives To estimate the incidence of pulmonary deterioration in adult pulmonary
      Langerhans cell histiocytosis To assess the impact of tobacco discontinuation Study Design
      Multicentric prospective cohort study Main endpoint: Pulmonary deterioration Sample size : 40
      patients
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
