    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Pulmonary Langerhans cell histiocytosis diagnosed within the past 48 months

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Age &lt; 18

          -  Deep pulmonary dysfunction (CPT&lt; 60%, FEV1&lt; 30%, DLCO&lt; 30%, partial pressure of oxygen
             in arterial blood (PaO2)&lt; 60mmHg)

          -  No informed consent or consent withdrawal
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
